PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Industry of ROBERT (BOB) McLEOD, of Yellowknife, Northwest Territories, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Tourism Commission to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Robert Fessenden, whose term has expired.
